des: When you're making a decision that could change the course of your life, knowledge is an invaluable tool. From a Q&A session with a virtual recruiter where you can get answers to your top questions, to an in-depth personality quiz on Navy jobs, My Navy Journey is here to educate you on all aspects of life as a Sailor to help you make the best and most informed decision possible.
